des: BANDTANGO New Alternative First At BANDTANGO we are changing the landscape of music and publishing. When you listen to us you are helping us with a very important mission. We want to be the Robinhood of the music industry. Leveling the playing field for artists and making sure monies end up getting distributed in a fair and transparent way. There is more to come. . . Sit back listen and if you have questions don't hesitate to reach out to info@bandtangocc.com.
